Texts.Eng: A control console of Skath origin. Press all the buttons!
Texts.Chs: 起源于绘世者的控制台。按所有的按钮！

Texts.Eng: This console was built to control a variety of electronics. Like any other console, it's encrypted and only readable by the Skath.
Texts.Chs: 这个控制台是用来控制各种电子设备的。与任何其他控制台一样，它是加密的，并且只能由绘世者读取。
